{
  "stem": "26142.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- and people from the surrounding the communities that heard that this and this rabbi is visiting here-- they would come-- come to greet the rabbi and to get a blessing.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That was the--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On the-- on the-- on the holidays, yes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't-- not always.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No, I don't think she did.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father was in the lumber business.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We-- we-- we owned a lumber mill.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My father owned a-- a-- over 500 acres of forest and a lot of land.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and-- the-- the business-- the business was selling wholesale and also retail building materials.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The-- the lumber-- the wholesale lumber-- was shipped by river.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Hungary was-- has no lumber whatsoever.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so they were very hungry for-- for lumber, for building materials.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the way we-- my father used to the business with company that was in Budapest, in Hungary.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we were in Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But-- when we shipped the lumber to them, by the river Riga, it went 80 kilometers to the city of Khust and, of course, more-- more streams were-- got into this, until it fell into the Tisza River.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The Tisza River was already a big river.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You could ship logs.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They would-- they were tied together, 10 or eight or 10 logs.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And the logs would be like 18, 20 meters-- which is like, meters is-- 20 meters would be about 60 feet long.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It-- this was very, very interesting work.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Whole logs, the way they tie them-- they tie them together with special-- not-- not ropes, but they made-- they made the ropes out of-- out of-- young-- young-- twine-- not twine--",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From twigs.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But they burned it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a whole process how they did that.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
